## Naming Convention

**Markdown files**: `{slug}.md`
- kebab-case
- descriptive of content
- Examples: `37-signals-in-datacenter.md`, `consulting-to-product-ideas.md`, `ai-efficiency-mindset.md`

**Cover images**: `{slug}.cover.png`
- Must match the markdown slug
- `.cover.png` suffix indicates it's a cover/hero image
- Examples: `37-signals-in-datacenter.cover.png`, `consulting-to-product-ideas.cover.png`

**Inline images** (if any): `{slug}.png` or `{slug}-{descriptor}.png`
- No `.cover` suffix
- Used for images embedded in content

